c: 57
v: 13
t: "On the Day the hypocrites— Men and women, will say to the believers: \"Wait for us! Let us get something (a light) from your Light!\" It will be said: \"(You) go back to the rear! Then seek a light (where you can)!\" So, a wall will be put between them, with a gate in it. Within it (the wall) will be mercy throughout, and outside and all alongside of it, will be (anger and) punishment"